snippet.title: Paper Animal RPG Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description: Featured in Wholesome Direct, Paper Animal RPG is a cute roguelite RPG that just went live on Kickstarter! "Inspired by Paper Mario, Mario & Luigi, and the Pokémon Mystery Dungeon series." https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/paperanimalrpg/paper-animal-rpg #indiegames #gaming #kickstarter
